description:
ExternalGNodeBFunction:  Metadata about external gNodeB functions in a RAN network.

dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the gNodeB.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2:  Redundant Cell ID.
Id3:  Likely an internal identifier; purpose unclear from sample data.
Id4:  External gNodeB function ID, possibly a composite key.
vsDataType: Data type identifier.
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.gNodeBIdLength: Length of the gNodeB ID.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.userLabel: User-friendly label for the gNodeB function.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.createdBy: Entity that created the record.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.eNBVlanPortRef: Reference to eNB VLAN port (appears empty in sample data).
ExternalGNodeBFunction.gNodeBPlmnId: PLMN ID of the gNodeB (appears empty in sample data).
ExternalGNodeBFunction.externalGNodeBFunctionId: Unique identifier of the external gNodeB function.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.dirDataPathAvail: Indicates whether a direct data path is available.
ExternalGNodeBFunction.gNodeBId:  gNodeB ID.
